The '''portaak leaf''' was a type of leaf found on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. Portaak leaf was edible, usually being roasted over [[Lammas/Legends|lammas]] [[Wood/Legends|wood]]. As both were available exclusively on Haruun Kal, both fetched a high price offworld.

The leaf was also the source of [[portaak amber]], and was eaten by [[grasser]]s.

